quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,65,( tum har barsaat mein dekhte ho ke ) Allah ne aasman se pani barsaya aur yaka yak murda pari hui zameen mein uss ki badolat jaan daal di yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai suneney walon ke liye
16,66,"aur tumahray liye maweshion mein bhi aik sabaq mojood hai unn ke pait se gobar aur khoon ke darmain hum aik cheez tumhe pilate hain, yani khalis doodh, jo peenay walon ke liye nihayat khoo sh gawaar hai"
16,67,( isi terhan ) khajoor ke darakhton aur angoor ki belon se bhi hum aik cheez tumhe pilate hain jisay tum nasha aawar bhi bana letay ho aur pak rizaq bhi yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai aqal se kaam lainay walon ke liye
16,68,"aur dekho, tumahray rab ne shehad ki makhi par yeh baat wahi kar di ke pahoron mein, aur darakhton mein, aur tatkyun par charhai hui belon mein"
16,69,apne chattay bana aur har terhan ke phalon ka ras choos aur apne rab ki hamwar ki hui raahon par chalti reh iss makhi ke andar se rang barang ka aik sharbat nikalta hai jis mein Shifa hai logon ke liye yaqeenan is mein bhi aik nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
16,70,"aur dekho, Allah ne tum ko peda kya, phir woh tum ko mout deta hai, aur tum mein se koi bad tareen Umar ko pouncha diya jata hai taakay sab kuch jan-nay ke baad phir kuch nah jaane haq yeh hai ke Allah hi ilm mein bhi kaamil hai aur qudrat mein bhi"
16,71,"aur dekho, Allah ne tum mein se baaz ko baaz par rizaq mein fazeelat ataa ki hai phir jin logon ko yeh fazeelat di gayi hai woh aisay nahi hain ke apna rizaq apne ghulamoo ki taraf phair diya karte hon taakay dono is rizaq mein barabar ke hissa daar ban jayen to kya Allah hi ka ahsaan maan-ne se inn logon ko inkaar hai ?"
16,72,aur woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumahray liye tumhari hum jins biwiyan banayen aur isi ne un biwion se tumhe betay potay ataa kiye aur achi achi cheezein tumhe khanay ko den phir kya yeh log ( yeh sab kuch dekhte aur jantay hue bhi ) baatil ko mantay hain aur Allah ke ahsaan ka inkaar karte hain
